System  : FreeBSD 4.3-STABLE
Perl    : 5.6.1
Gtk     : 0.7005
Tk      : 800.022
Event   : 0.81
IO::Pty : 0.01

All tests successful.
Files=26, Tests=494, 83 wallclock secs ( 7.78 cusr +  0.55 csys =  8.33 CPU)

